@startuml
skinparam actorStyle awesome

actor "ユーザー" as User

' --- 地獄の階層構造 ---
box "nix develop を連打 (階層化)" #F9F9F9
    participant "Bash (Original)" as b1
    participant "Subshell (nix-1)" as b2
    participant "Subshell (nix-2)" as b3
end box

' --- direnvのスマートな管理 ---
box "direnv (階層なし・自動切替)" #E6F3FF
    participant "Shell (Top)" as d1
end box

== Nix Develop (手動連打) ==
User -> b1 : nix develop
b1 -> b2 : 入る
User -> b2 : nix develop
b2 -> b3 : 入る
User -> b3 : (ここで作業)
User -> b3 : exit (1回目)
User -> b2 : exit (2回目)
note right of b3 : 階層が深すぎて\nExitを繰り返す必要がある

== Direnv (自動ロード) ==
User -> d1 : cd ./project_A
d1 -> d1 : direnv load (自動)
User -> d1 : (作業)
User -> d1 : cd ..
d1 -> d1 : direnv unload (自動)
note right of d1 : 階層を潜らないので\nExitの概念自体がない

@enduml